<div class="topclear">
<h2 class="page-title">Fellows Program</h2>
<p>The <strong>Internet2 Fellows Program</strong> offers qualified persons the opportunity to work full- or part-time on a collaborative project with an Internet2 staff member, with whom the project's contents are jointly described and proposed. The project start date, fraction of time, and duration&mdash;which can range from three months to one year&mdash;are selected in advance. The program is administered by the Internet2 Office of the CTO, but Fellows may collaborate with Internet2 staff in any Internet2 division, subject to the final approval of the division vice president.</p>
<p>Persons of exceptional stature in the Internet2 community who wish to work with Internet2 on wide-ranging and strategic issues may apply to be an Internet2 Presidential Fellow. Presidential Fellows report directly to the Internet2 CEO.</p>
</div><!-- /topclear-->
<div id="container">
<div id="col1">
		  <div class="block">
          <div class="block-header learn-more"><h2>Learn More</h2></div>
